reviewText: Item as described and shipped promptly Recommend to all A+++ Thanks
awesome episode on Gettysburg. only one episode but still good.
This dvd was great. They did an excellent job picking the different  pieces needed for the museum in Gettysburg. I liked how they got to participate in an actual reenactment.
Good show, I wish there were more episodes per box.

Best of the series. Highly recommended to those who have or are going to visit Gettysburg and the Gettysburg Museum of History. Have visited more than once and have enjoyed the museum and talking to Eric Dorr the museum curator and owner.  Anyone interested in the Civil War will more than enjoy this program and the Pickers.
Love American Pickers. Fast shipping. New product as described.
The history of the items found was interesting.
As much as I love this show. And this is a great episode. Cannot give it more then 3 stars because it is only one episode.
